74
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:19,000
The P sound point is that raised circle on the top right that

75
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,600
make up the sounds "PA, PI, PU, PE, PO"!

76
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,300
